OL,3,CNHS maintenance backlog soars to more
OL,4,Cthan #1.3bn, figures show
OL,6,FThe cost of the maintenance backlog in
OL,7,FScotland's NHS has risen to more than
OL,8,F#1.3 billion, figures show.
OL,10,FData released following a freedom of
OL,11,Finformation request from the Scottish
OL,12,FConservatives shows it would take
OL,13,F#1.335 billion to clear the
OL,14,Fmaintenance waiting list, according to
OL,15,Fthe Scottish Government.
OL,17,FThe figure, which comes from April
OL,18,Fthis year so may now be even higher,
OL,19,Fis an increase from #1.1 billion at
OL,20,Fthe end of 2022, according to a report
OL,21,Fby Audit Scotland.
