OL,6,F"In the space of a few months, this
OL,7,Fbill has escalated by over #200
OL,8,Fmillion on the SNP's watch. These
OL,9,Ffigures are a damning indictment of
OL,10,Fhow the nationalists have shamefully
OL,11,Fneglected our health service over the
OL,12,Fpast 17 years.
OL,14,F"Successive SNP health secretaries
OL,15,Fhave had their eye off the ball and
OL,16,Fallowed crucial health care services
OL,17,Fto fall into a total state of
OL,18,Fdisrepair, which ultimately impacts
OL,19,Fpatients and staff, as well as health
OL,20,Fboards' budgets.
