OL,6,F"In light of these figures, it is
OL,7,Flittle wonder independent auditors
OL,8,Fthink the SNP have no vision for our
OL,9,FNHS when they can't even support its
OL,10,Fbasic upkeep.
OL,12,F"The eye-watering sum of money that is
OL,13,Fgoing to be needed to tackle these
OL,14,Fmaintenance costs only takes more
OL,15,Fmoney away from the front line, where
OL,16,Fthe SNP are overseeing record waiting
OL,17,Flists and worsening A&E waiting times."
